'''公民科技'''是指一类技术（尤其是信息技术），此类技术能够促使公民参与公益事业发展，加强公民之间的交流，改善政府的基础设施建设，促使政府和国家变得更高效。“公民科技”包含公民应用、平台、以及实现上述目标的其他软件。<ref>{{cite web|title=Civic Tech: Entrepreneurship Opportunities|url=http://codeforamerica.org/startups/civic-entrepreneurship-2014/|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140727043407/http://codeforamerica.org/startups/civic-entrepreneurship-2014/|archivedate=2014-07-27|accessdate=2016-11-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Nick Bilton: New York Times: Changing Government and Tech With Geeks|url=http://bits.blogs.nytimes.com/2010/07/06/changing-government-and-tech-with-geeks/?_php=true&_type=blogs&_php=true&_type=blogs&_r=1|accessdate=2016-11-10|archive-date=2018-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180220212753/https://bits.blogs.nytimes.com/2010/07/06/changing-government-and-tech-with-geeks/?_php=true&_type=blogs&_php=true&_type=blogs&_r=1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=But What Is "Civic"?|url=http://civichall.org/civicist/what-is-civic/|accessdate=2016-11-10|archive-date=2016-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160711150856/http://civichall.org/civicist/what-is-civic/|dead-url=yes}}</ref> It encompasses [[civic_application|civic application]]s, platforms supporting government bodies, institutions and other software enabling those goals.

